The '''European Christian Political Foundation''' (ECPF) is a Political foundation at European level, and the official foundation/think tank of the [[European Christian Political Movement]] (ECPM), founded in 2011.
The ECPF supports and underpins the ECPM especially in terms of political content by European co-operation and the introduction of analysis, ideas and policy options. The ECPF shares the basic program and Christian values of the ECPM. As association the ECPF welcomes thinktanks, NGO’s and individual politicians as members if they agree with these values and the Christian-democrat principles as expressed in the basic program.
The ECPF is based in [[Amersfoort]], [[Netherlands]]. President of the board is [[Davis Fieldsend]] from the [[United Kingdom]].
