The '''National Inventory of Dams''' (NID) is a congressionally authorized database documenting [[dam]]s in the United States and its territories.<ref name=data.gov/> It is maintained and published by the [[US Army Corps of Engineers]].<ref name=data.gov/> It contains information about each dam's location, size, purpose, type, last inspection and regulatory facts.<ref name=data.gov>{{cite web|title=National Inventory of Dams|url=https://catalog.data.gov/dataset/national-inventory-of-dams|website=[[Data.gov]]|publisher=[[U.S. Government]]|accessdate=24 September 2017|format=html}}{{PD-notice}}</ref>

