{{blockquote|text=We wanted to bring back many (of the original characters) into the story but since we jumped off to another topic, another institution, which is media, we wanted to refresh the cast of characters. What we enjoyed in the first movie is how we put together also the kind of casting that we got, (meaning) all of those actors we admired. We wanted to also have the same kind of feel. We brought a lot of actors that could possibly do new and refreshing kind of roles.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Valeza |first1=Karen |title=''On The Job'' now a mini-series |url=http://entertainment.mb.com.ph/2016/11/16/on-the-job-now-a-mini-series/ |accessdate=June 19, 2017 |newspaper=[[Manila Bulletin]] |date=December 7, 2016 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161117150257/http://entertainment.mb.com.ph/2016/11/16/on-the-job-now-a-mini-series/ |archivedate=November 17, 2016 }}</ref>}}

